259
00:21:30,824 --> 00:21:31,304
It doesn't.

260
00:21:31,824 --> 00:21:32,304
It doesn't?

261
00:21:32,705 --> 00:21:33,225
Alright.

262
00:21:34,185 --> 00:21:34,505
Miss,

263
00:21:34,505 --> 00:21:35,665
